## Conventions

- **File names**: kebab-case (`use-auth.ts`, `loading-screen.tsx`)
- **Component names**: PascalCase in code (`function LoadingScreen()`)
- **Imports**: Prefer `@/` alias for all internal imports (e.g. `@/components/logo`, `@/hooks/use-auth`, `@/utils/axios`). BaseUrl paths (`components/logo`, `hooks/use-auth`) are acceptable for short paths. Never use relative `../../` beyond one level.
- Components use Tailwind classes via `className` and `cn()`
- Colors and spacing from CSS variables (e.g. `--primary`, `--muted`) or Tailwind theme
- Environment variables prefixed with `VITE_`
- No `React.FC` ‚Äî use plain function components with typed props
- Prefer `interface` over `type` for component props
